What a pity.

00:16:01.861 --> 00:16:03.581
I fail to drive a wedge between you.

00:16:04.022 --> 00:16:04.861
Otherwise,

00:16:05.062 --> 00:16:06.981
I wouldn't need to make such efforts.

00:16:07.062 --> 00:16:08.662
I advise you to stop now.

00:16:08.662 --> 00:16:10.142
Stop now?

00:16:10.821 --> 00:16:12.941
Stop what?

00:16:13.262 --> 00:16:14.581
The Ascension Array

00:16:14.741 --> 00:16:15.680
will never stop

00:16:15.680 --> 00:16:16.941
because of the two of you.

00:16:19.782 --> 00:16:20.621
Kong Hou,

00:16:21.221 --> 00:16:22.741
only Zhong Xi's death

00:16:22.861 --> 00:16:23.981
will make you obedient

00:16:23.981 --> 00:16:25.382
to activate the array with me.

00:16:25.621 --> 00:16:26.621
I remember

00:16:27.701 --> 00:16:28.981
I planted a Gu parasite

00:16:28.981 --> 00:16:30.542
inside you.

00:16:41.741 --> 00:16:43.662
You've expelled the Gu parasite?

00:16:45.341 --> 00:16:46.262
So,

00:16:47.062 --> 00:16:48.621
you've restored your spiritual core?

00:16:50.022 --> 00:16:51.182
I forgot to mention

00:16:51.581 --> 00:16:52.581
my cultivation level

00:16:52.581 --> 00:16:53.861
has surpassed Void Unity.

00:16:53.902 --> 00:16:55.662
Even you've restored
your spiritual core,

00:16:55.782 --> 00:16:57.422
you can't defeat me either.

00:16:57.581 --> 00:16:59.701
I know my current strength

00:17:00.422 --> 00:17:01.941
can't kill you,

00:17:02.221 --> 00:17:03.861
but even so,

00:17:05.062 --> 00:17:05.901
I'll fight you

00:17:05.901 --> 00:17:07.421
to the end.

00:17:07.542 --> 00:17:08.621
Seek death?

00:17:09.088 --> 00:17:10.141
I'll grant you.

00:17:10.421 --> 00:17:11.782
Don't harm him.

00:17:12.141 --> 00:17:12.861
Move!

00:17:13.821 --> 00:17:14.581
Kong Hou.

00:17:30.141 --> 00:17:31.262
Zhong Xi!

00:17:44.141 --> 00:17:44.942
Zhong Xi.

00:17:46.222 --> 00:17:47.181
Zhong Xi.

00:17:49.381 --> 00:17:50.821
Zhong Xi, look at me.

00:17:51.022 --> 00:17:51.942
Are you okay?

00:17:52.022 --> 00:17:53.262
Don't scare me.

00:17:53.661 --> 00:17:55.062
You'll be fine.

00:17:55.222 --> 00:17:57.181
I won't let anything happen to you.

00:17:58.101 --> 00:18:00.782
- Zhong Xi.
- I didn't expect I'm so useless.

00:18:01.901 --> 00:18:02.621
Take care

00:18:03.821 --> 00:18:04.942
of yourself.

00:18:05.462 --> 00:18:07.262
No!

00:18:07.861 --> 00:18:09.222
Don't leave me!

00:18:10.901 --> 00:18:12.861
Don't leave me!

00:18:13.421 --> 00:18:15.168
I won't let you die.

00:18:15.381 --> 00:18:16.341
Zhong Xi.

00:18:17.022 --> 00:18:20.222
- Don't leave me.
- Kong Hou, stop it.

00:18:20.621 --> 00:18:21.742
He's dead.

00:18:21.821 --> 00:18:22.661
I advise you

00:18:22.661 --> 00:18:24.062
to obey.

00:18:24.742 --> 00:18:26.062
After ascension,

00:18:26.222 --> 00:18:27.782
you can do

00:18:27.861 --> 00:18:29.222
whatever you want.

00:18:29.381 --> 00:18:31.702
But if you defy me,

00:18:31.861 --> 00:18:33.381
and I'll make you

00:18:34.022 --> 00:18:35.982
suffer.

00:18:41.181 --> 00:18:42.062
Zhong Xi.

00:18:44.462 --> 00:18:45.222
Zhong Xi.

00:18:48.462 --> 00:18:50.062
I won't let you die.

00:18:50.302 --> 00:18:51.581
There must be a way.

00:18:52.462 --> 00:18:54.022
They must be a way to save you.

00:18:54.661 --> 00:18:55.782
They must be.

00:18:56.542 --> 00:18:57.821
Master Huang Qi.

00:18:59.062 --> 00:19:00.821
He once said

00:19:01.381 --> 00:19:03.062
the Phoenix Essence could

00:19:03.502 --> 00:19:04.702
save you.

00:19:06.222 --> 00:19:08.222
As long as I extract
my Phoenix Essence...

00:19:11.661 --> 00:19:12.581
Zhong Xi.

00:19:14.942 --> 00:19:16.542
I will definitely save you.

00:20:02.782 --> 00:20:03.742
Zhong Xi.

00:20:06.782 --> 00:20:08.621
After extracting the Phoenix Essence,

00:20:09.742 --> 00:20:11.181
my time will be running out.

00:20:12.341 --> 00:20:13.062
But

00:20:15.821 --> 00:20:18.022
you must live on for me.

00:20:32.621 --> 00:20:33.942
Everything's done?

00:20:37.621 --> 00:20:38.341
Kong Hou,

00:20:38.821 --> 00:20:39.702
cheer up.

00:20:40.381 --> 00:20:41.702
After ascension,

00:20:41.901 --> 00:20:43.982
these worldly worries will vanish.

00:20:44.302 --> 00:20:44.942
Look!

00:20:45.421 --> 00:20:47.062
We're about to ascend.

00:20:48.821 --> 00:20:50.222
I've been waiting for this day

00:20:50.742 --> 00:20:52.222
for so long.

00:20:54.702 --> 00:20:56.421
Had we reunited earlier,

00:20:56.661 --> 00:20:58.462
we might have ascended long ago.

00:21:00.141 --> 00:21:01.141
Without me,

00:21:01.581 --> 00:21:03.222
you could still ascend.

00:21:03.302 --> 00:21:04.502
It's not the same.

00:21:04.861 --> 00:21:06.502
Our joint cultivation,

00:21:06.542 --> 00:21:07.581
and blood sacrifices

00:21:07.581 --> 00:21:09.262
of the Ten Great Sects' elite disciples,

00:21:09.542 --> 00:21:11.222
will make the ascension smoothly.

00:21:11.861 --> 00:21:13.421
If our parents knew

00:21:13.861 --> 00:21:15.861
we siblings work together like this,

00:21:16.062 --> 00:21:17.262
they'd be pleased.

00:21:20.742 --> 00:21:22.262
The dead are gone.

00:21:22.462 --> 00:21:23.742
What's there to be pleased?

00:21:26.421 --> 00:21:28.782
Fine, whatever.

00:21:28.942 --> 00:21:30.742
I have matters to attend to.

00:21:30.982 --> 00:21:32.702
You stay here and figure out

00:21:32.901 --> 00:21:34.062
if it's worth it

00:21:34.782 --> 00:21:35.782
for a man.

00:22:05.702 --> 00:22:06.462
(I...)

00:22:09.302 --> 00:22:10.542
(I'm still alive.)

00:22:17.821 --> 00:22:18.821
Zhong Xi!

00:22:19.421 --> 00:22:20.341
Look at me.

00:22:20.381 --> 00:22:21.661
Don't scare me.

00:22:22.062 --> 00:22:23.381
You'll be fine.

00:22:23.542 --> 00:22:25.381
I won't let you die.

00:22:25.821 --> 00:22:27.942
(Wasn't I killed by Jiusu?)

00:22:28.262 --> 00:22:29.421
(How is this possible?)

00:22:34.462 --> 00:22:35.542
(Kong Hou.)

00:22:36.861 --> 00:22:37.861
(Kong Hou.)

00:23:07.782 --> 00:23:08.982
Whose Heavenly Tribulation?

00:23:10.542 --> 00:23:13.062
Sovereign Kong Hou?

00:23:14.661 --> 00:23:15.942
Kong Hou?

00:23:17.702 --> 00:23:19.942
How could she withstand
such thunder strikes?

00:23:20.742 --> 00:23:22.222
Any misstep

00:23:22.782 --> 00:23:24.302
would kill her.

00:23:28.621 --> 00:23:30.302
Who's advancing their cultivation level?

00:23:30.621 --> 00:23:32.901
Only a few people
in the Dark Cultivator Hall can

00:23:32.982 --> 00:23:34.302
advance their cultivation level.

00:23:34.982 --> 00:23:35.821
Is it...

00:23:36.222 --> 00:23:37.341
It's Zhong Xi.

00:23:39.421 --> 00:23:40.421
Impossible.

00:23:40.861 --> 00:23:42.022
The Phoenix Essence

00:23:42.022 --> 00:23:43.502
could revive the dead.

00:23:43.861 --> 00:23:45.222
But it requires three days

00:23:45.341 --> 00:23:46.421
to take effect.

00:23:46.821 --> 00:23:49.462
He's revived already?

00:23:50.141 --> 00:23:51.542
But how can he withstand

00:23:51.661 --> 00:23:53.262
the thunder strikes?

00:24:29.502 --> 00:24:30.222
Kong Hou.

00:24:30.542 --> 00:24:32.581
Were you advancing
your cultivation level just now?

00:24:33.141 --> 00:24:33.861
No.

00:24:34.462 --> 00:24:35.742
Such thunder strikes...

00:24:35.782 --> 00:24:37.062
It must be Zhong Xi.

00:24:37.222 --> 00:24:38.336
He's dead.

00:24:38.581 --> 00:24:39.742
How could he do so?

00:24:39.861 --> 00:24:41.542
You're being delusional.

00:24:41.621 --> 00:24:43.542
Then what's going on
with the thunder strikes?

00:24:43.621 --> 00:24:44.341
Wu Bei.

00:24:44.502 --> 00:24:46.141
Are you questioning me again?

00:24:48.062 --> 00:24:48.942
I wouldn't dare.

00:24:49.421 --> 00:24:51.262
You clearly do.

00:24:51.942 --> 00:24:53.462
Another word,

00:24:53.542 --> 00:24:55.702
and I'll sacrifice you to the array.

00:24:56.421 --> 00:24:58.022
The ascension is approaching.

00:24:58.181 --> 00:25:00.341
I won't allow anyone

00:25:00.542 --> 00:25:02.062
to disrupt my ascension.

00:25:03.101 --> 00:25:04.621
The Ten Great Sects' disciples

00:25:04.621 --> 00:25:06.141
must be nearby now.

00:25:06.421 --> 00:25:07.302
Jiusu,

00:25:07.421 --> 00:25:08.421
no time to waste.

00:25:08.581 --> 00:25:10.222
Let's depart now

00:25:10.341 --> 00:25:12.181
to avoid complications.

00:25:39.821 --> 00:25:40.581
What's this?

00:25:40.621 --> 00:25:41.661
A messenger talisman?

00:25:41.742 --> 00:25:42.702
Why is it so weird?

00:25:43.022 --> 00:25:43.904
It is Liuguang Sect's

00:25:43.904 --> 00:25:44.581
talisman.

00:25:44.702 --> 00:25:47.381
An emergency messenger talisman
requires heart's blood to activate.

00:25:47.502 --> 00:25:48.576
Young Master must be

00:25:48.576 --> 00:25:49.581
in danger.

00:25:49.702 --> 00:25:50.661
I need to go with you.

00:25:50.661 --> 00:25:51.581
No, it's too dangerous.

00:25:51.621 --> 00:25:52.462
Kong Hou told us

00:25:52.581 --> 00:25:53.542
to wait here for her.

00:25:53.581 --> 00:25:54.341
If she arrives

00:25:54.341 --> 00:25:55.982
and finds no one here, that'd be bad.

00:25:56.062 --> 00:25:57.581
Well, I'll go find Young Master.

00:25:57.621 --> 00:25:58.621
You'd stay here.

00:25:58.982 --> 00:25:59.942
Alright.

00:26:02.901 --> 00:26:03.742
Be careful.

00:26:07.942 --> 00:26:10.181
Be careful! I'll wait for your return.

00:26:12.542 --> 00:26:13.542
Move!

00:26:14.101 --> 00:26:15.942
Move! Hurry!

00:26:15.942 --> 00:26:16.782
Hurry up!

00:26:16.782 --> 00:26:18.581
- Hurry!
- Or I'll kill you!

00:26:19.542 --> 00:26:20.542
Don't touch me.

00:26:21.341 --> 00:26:22.942
Let me tell you the truth.

00:26:22.982 --> 00:26:23.821
Even Zhong Xi

00:26:23.821 --> 00:26:24.982
is no match for us.

00:26:25.101 --> 00:26:26.502
How dare you oppose us?

00:26:26.581 --> 00:26:27.222
Move!

00:26:39.742 --> 00:26:40.942
Master Zhong Xi.

00:26:42.341 --> 00:26:43.661
Don't stay here.

00:26:43.702 --> 00:26:44.861
You two go back now.

00:26:45.022 --> 00:26:45.782
- What about you?
- But...

00:26:45.782 --> 00:26:46.861
I'll go save Kong Hou.

00:26:47.062 --> 00:26:47.942
I'll go with you.

00:26:47.942 --> 00:26:48.621
No way.

00:26:48.782 --> 00:26:50.048
Jiusu's cultivation level

00:26:50.048 --> 00:26:51.141
has reached Void Unity.

00:26:51.302 --> 00:26:52.502
I'll go alone.

00:26:52.982 --> 00:26:54.381
You two go back now.

00:26:54.421 --> 00:26:55.262
Get reinforcements.

00:26:55.502 --> 00:26:56.302
Go now.

00:26:56.421 --> 00:26:57.101
Alright.

00:26:59.101 --> 00:26:59.808
- Go!
- Go!

00:26:59.808 --> 00:27:00.576
- Hurry!
- Hurry!

00:27:00.864 --> 00:27:01.472
Hurry!

00:27:21.341 --> 00:27:22.462
Zhong Xi is still alive.

00:27:22.542 --> 00:27:24.421
He rescued all the disciples.

00:27:27.381 --> 00:27:29.141
My lord, terrible news!

00:27:29.341 --> 00:27:31.341
Zhong Xi released
all the sect disciples!

00:27:32.742 --> 00:27:33.581
What did you say?

00:27:33.742 --> 00:27:36.101
Zhong Xi released
all the sect disciples!

00:27:37.381 --> 00:27:38.621
Wasn't he dead?

00:27:39.022 --> 00:27:40.262
You were there

00:27:40.262 --> 00:27:41.621
when he died.

00:27:42.181 --> 00:27:43.421
And I possess no power

00:27:43.421 --> 00:27:44.742
to revive the dead.

00:27:44.942 --> 00:27:46.661
Then why is he still alive

00:27:46.821 --> 00:27:48.302
and even rescued the disciples?

00:27:48.502 --> 00:27:50.621
Your people

00:27:50.861 --> 00:27:52.141
escort the disciples.

00:27:53.022 --> 00:27:53.782
What now?

00:27:54.062 --> 00:27:55.702
The disciples

00:27:55.702 --> 00:27:57.101
escaped?

00:27:57.661 --> 00:27:59.742
You claim Zhong Xi rescued them,

00:28:00.022 --> 00:28:01.181
so where's the evidence?

00:28:01.421 --> 00:28:03.302
Quite eloquent.

00:28:03.381 --> 00:28:05.421
You're still making excuses.

00:28:05.861 --> 00:28:06.742
My lord,

00:28:06.982 --> 00:28:08.421
Kong Hou has never

00:28:08.421 --> 00:28:09.661
truly submitted to you,

00:28:09.661 --> 00:28:10.784
nor has she ever

00:28:10.784 --> 00:28:12.621
truly sided with you.

00:28:13.581 --> 00:28:14.462
Kong Hou,

00:28:14.942 --> 00:28:16.101
after his death,

00:28:16.341 --> 00:28:17.381
you stayed in that cave

00:28:17.381 --> 00:28:18.341
with him for a period.

00:28:18.502 --> 00:28:19.341
What did you do?

00:28:19.581 --> 00:28:21.421
If you judge me guilty

00:28:21.421 --> 00:28:22.942
based on a messenger talisman,

00:28:24.421 --> 00:28:25.861
then I have nothing to say.

00:28:27.302 --> 00:28:28.022
Guards!

00:28:28.262 --> 00:28:29.222
Go check the cave.

00:28:29.421 --> 00:28:30.181
My lord,

00:28:30.542 --> 00:28:32.141
I'll go check it myself.

00:28:37.101 --> 00:28:38.502
(It seems everyone's safe now.)

00:28:39.141 --> 00:28:40.502
(Now I can rest easy.)

00:28:52.022 --> 00:28:52.901
My lord,

00:28:53.062 --> 00:28:54.782
Zhong Xi isn't in the cave at all.

00:28:54.782 --> 00:28:55.901
He escaped.

00:28:57.381 --> 00:28:58.222
Kong Hou,

00:28:58.621 --> 00:28:59.821
how do you explain this?

00:29:00.181 --> 00:29:01.702
Where have you hidden him?

00:29:02.861 --> 00:29:03.702
Kong Hou,

00:29:04.181 --> 00:29:05.901
I demand an explanation now.

00:29:07.901 --> 00:29:09.782
You would rather trust him

00:29:09.982 --> 00:29:11.421
than me, your sister.

00:29:11.861 --> 00:29:12.821
Perhaps

00:29:12.942 --> 00:29:14.542
someone

00:29:14.702 --> 00:29:16.381
intentionally hid

00:29:16.381 --> 00:29:17.341
Zhong Xi's corpse

00:29:17.542 --> 00:29:19.022
to frame me.

00:29:19.581 --> 00:29:20.381
If you

00:29:20.381 --> 00:29:21.581
refuse to trust me,

00:29:22.621 --> 00:29:24.022
then punish me.

00:29:24.302 --> 00:29:25.262
My lord,

00:29:25.621 --> 00:29:27.022
Kong Hou must have colluded

00:29:27.022 --> 00:29:27.861
with Zhong Xi

00:29:27.982 --> 00:29:29.141
to ruin

00:29:29.141 --> 00:29:30.621
your ascension.

00:29:31.661 --> 00:29:32.341
Wu Bei,

00:29:32.821 --> 00:29:33.581
I suspect

00:29:33.821 --> 00:29:35.542
you hid

00:29:35.542 --> 00:29:36.502
Zhong Xi's corpse

00:29:36.901 --> 00:29:38.381
to frame me

00:29:39.222 --> 00:29:40.062
and sow discord

00:29:40.062 --> 00:29:41.942
between Jiusu and me,

00:29:42.381 --> 00:29:45.462
so you can ascend with him.

00:29:45.742 --> 00:29:47.581
What a scheme!

00:29:48.302 --> 00:29:50.621
But remember.

00:29:51.022 --> 00:29:52.381
Without me,

00:29:54.262 --> 00:29:55.702
none of you will ascend.

00:29:55.982 --> 00:29:56.861
What?

00:29:56.982 --> 00:29:57.901
Even now,

00:29:57.901 --> 00:29:59.861
you still try to slander me?

00:30:01.062 --> 00:30:01.901
My lord,

00:30:02.341 --> 00:30:04.421
I swear I harbor no such intentions.

00:30:04.502 --> 00:30:06.421
- We cannot spare Kong Hou.
- Wu Bei.

00:30:06.942 --> 00:30:08.462
How dare you!

00:30:08.861 --> 00:30:10.661
You've repeatedly framed me.

00:30:11.022 --> 00:30:11.702
And now

00:30:11.861 --> 00:30:13.421
you even try to distort the facts?

00:30:13.421 --> 00:30:14.141
Enough!

00:30:18.341 --> 00:30:19.392
The ascension's coming,

00:30:19.742 --> 00:30:21.381
stop the quarrel.

00:30:21.661 --> 00:30:22.381
Guards!

00:30:22.702 --> 00:30:23.782
Take Kong Hou away.

00:30:24.101 --> 00:30:24.942
Who dares?

00:30:31.502 --> 00:30:32.381
My lord,

00:30:32.742 --> 00:30:34.421
this is suspicious.

00:30:34.621 --> 00:30:36.381
We cannot spare Kong Hou.

00:30:37.381 --> 00:30:38.542
I need her

00:30:39.181 --> 00:30:41.141
Phoenix Essence for ascension.

00:30:42.222 --> 00:30:43.341
We'll talk later.

00:30:44.702 --> 00:30:46.181
(Yunhua Sect)
Kong Hou,

00:30:46.581 --> 00:30:48.421
my beloved disciple.

00:30:48.861 --> 00:30:50.861
How could you do so?

00:30:51.141 --> 00:30:53.302
- I...
- Master Wang Tong.

00:30:53.302 --> 00:30:53.821
Tan Feng

00:30:53.821 --> 00:30:54.821
and Ling Hui are back.

00:30:54.821 --> 00:30:55.742
Really?

00:30:58.144 --> 00:30:58.656
Master.

00:30:58.656 --> 00:31:00.101
